Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ToAddA: <span> Don ƙara mai kunnawa ko mai hanawa, jawo da sauke abubuwa daga lissafin abubuwan ciki na ciki ko Na'urorin waje zuwa akwatin zance na Drop Component dace. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase1.ClickO: Danna kan hoto [photo} don ajiye canje-canje.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.U: <span> Yi amfani da sauƙi mai sauƙi don saita yanayi na waje (watau saƙon kwaikwayo). Za a iya bambanta matakai a yayin simfiti don ganin yadda canje-canje a cikin tsarin da ke cikin ainihin lokaci. Wannan yana da mahimmanci da bambancin yanayi na tsarin nazarin halittu da kuma lura da amsawarta. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.S: Zaɓi akwati da ke ƙasa da ganuwa [photo] icon don abubuwan da kake so su gani a kan Simulation Shafi. Hadawa kan lakabin lakabin zai nuna haskensa, yana ba ka damar gano wuri a cikin jimlar aikin!
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase1.C: Click {photo1} icon don fara samfurin. Kuna iya danna {photo2} don dakatar da kwaikwayo a kowane lokaci ko sake saita simfuri ta danna kan hoto [photo3}.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Danna kan {photo} icon don ƙirƙirar sabuwar gwaji. An sake sake yin gwaje-gwajen kai tsaye ta danna kan lakabin.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Use: <span> Yi amfani da sauƙi mai sauƙi don saita yanayi na waje (watau aikin kwaikwayo) don gwaji. Wannan daidai ne tare da kafa sakonnin waje na tsarin cibiyoyin halittu a cikin yanayinta, yana tasiriyar mayar da martani. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Cli: Danna kan {photo} iicon don fara simintin.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase1.Dos: <span> Shafuka masu jituwa ba za a iya haifar da su ba ga wani ɓangaren samfurin ta hanyar zaɓar abin da ya dace don Xis da Y-axis. Gaba ɗaya, an wakilci wani waje a kan X-axis (ƙwarƙiri mai juyayi) yayin da aka gyara sassan ciki a kan Y-axis (masu juyayi masu dogara). Ƙididdiga masu yawa-amsawa za a iya haifar da su daga gwaji guda. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouMayS: <span> Zaka iya bincika samfurin da take, bayanin, tags ko sunan sunadaran. Wata tambaya daya za ta bincika samfurori da aka wallafa, da rubutun na, da kuma rabawa tare da ni a lokaci daya. </ Span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.ChangeB: Canja a tsakanin List da Grid View
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.YouCanC: <span> Zaka iya canza ra'ayi tsakanin view list da duba grid </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsHomePhase2.InThisM: <span> A cikin wannan menu za ka iya shirya bayanin mai amfani naka, canza kalmarka ta sirri, da kuma bayananka. </ span>
JoyDashboardRide.joyrideStepsModelPhase2: <span> Yanayi (ko SubConditions) ana amfani dashi don yin kwaskwarima ko haɗin kai tsakanin ɗaya ko fiye abokan hulɗa. Danna kan karamin icon don buɗe Ƙunshin ka'idodin, ja da sauke abubuwan da aka dace a cikin akwatin zance (drop component) kuma saka idan Yanayin dole ne Aiki ko Mai aiki. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.ClickO: Ana yin amfani da alamomi da rubutu tare da yin amfani da Bayanan Ilimin. Danna kan {photo1} don ƙara abun ciki da {photo2} don ƙara haɗin. Kawai shigar da PubMed Identifier (PMID) don yin amfani da shi ba tare da hadewa ba. Za a iya ƙididdige bayanan da aka ba da shi kamar yadda aka buga da kuma irin bayanai. Kawai danna dama a kan mahimmanci kuma zaɓi tag da kake so ka ƙara.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Collab: Hadin gwiwa yana da mahimmanci ga sababbin binciken ta hanyar amfani da tsarin tsarin - kuma yana cikin zuciyar Cellive! Danna kan [photo] tana kai ka zuwa Shafin Shafin, yana ba ka damar ƙara abokan haɗin kai, ƙirƙirar haɗin gwaninta da kuma buga gwaje-gwaje.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsModelPhase2.Select: <span> Zaɓi bangaren da kake so a mutate. Danna akwatin a sau ɗaya shine maye gurbin haɓaka (wanda aka nuna ta wurin alamar ja), kuma danna akwatin sau sau biyu shine maye gurbin maye gurbin (wanda aka nuna ta alama ta kore). Danna ta hanyar sau uku yana kawar da maye gurbin. Za a iya gabatarwa a gaban ko a lokacin simintin kwaikwayo don ganin yadda canje-canjen da aka canza a ainihin lokaci. </ span>
Dashboard.joyrideStepsSimulationPhase2.C: Click {photo} don ƙirƙirar wata ƙasa ta farko. Da zarar an halicci wata ƙasa ta farko, ana nuna icon a cikin Ƙungiyoyi masu ciki. Daga wannan shafi, zaɓi abubuwan da kake son aiki a farkon simulation (t = 0).

Latsa {photo} don yin rikodin tsaftacewa. Gunkin zai kunna sau ɗaya bayan rikodi ya ci gaba. Canje-canje a yanayi na gwaji ko maye gurbi, da kuma lokuttan lokaci na lokaci-lokaci, an rubuta su kuma ana ajiye su a cikin ƙaddamarwar simintin, yana taimakawa sake yin gwaje-gwajen da aka saita.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Mul: <span> Ana iya zaɓar zaɓuɓɓuka masu yawa ta amfani da akwati. Da zarar an zaba, za ka iya cire, kwafi, ko sake gudanar da gwaje-gwajen a lokaci guda. Wannan yana da amfani sosai ga gwaje-gwajen sabuntawa bayan yin canje-canje ga tsari na tsarin samfurin. </ span>,
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Col: Latsa {photo} kusa da Simulation Flow: lakabi don ƙirƙirar ƙirar simulation. Baza a iya rubuta rikodin ƙwaƙwalwar bincike ba, sabili da haka, yanayi na waje (watau bayanai) ko maye gurbi, da kuma iyakar su (watau ma'anar lokaci-lokaci) dole ne a shirya su da hannu. Karanta ƙayyadaddun ƙaddamarwa don ƙarin bayani.
Dashboard.joyrideStepsAnalysisPhase2.Onc: <span> Da zarar kana da jadawalin da aka gabatar a nan za ka iya sauke Ɗaukar Harkokin Ayyukan Hanya kamar fayil ɗin PNG ta latsa nan. </ span>
